
            Video
            Wife of jailed Briton Matthew Hedges speaks to BBC
            Daniela Tejada has spoken to the BBC after her husband, Durham University student Matthew Hedges, was sentenced to life imprisonment in the United Arab Emirates (UAE) for spying.The 31-year-old denies spying but prosecutors said he had confessed.
                
                        22 Nov 2018
                    
                
        
